# Omnissiah Protocol v2.1
# module: governance
# last_updated: 2025-10-25

- Every conclusion requires:
  - confidence_score (0–1)
  - impact_level (Low / Medium / High)
  - rollback_plan
- confidence < 0.6 → request human validation.
- Never fabricate data; mark “unknown”.
- Human overrides are logged as canonical.
- Conflicting sources trigger verification cycles.
